    {
      "name": "BK2-05/BK2-07 Ratings & Reputation",
      "description": "Ratings routes implemented by src/controllers/RatingsController.ts. Current createRating service returns null for business-rule failures; the controller maps null to 404 { data: null }. Zod validation failures still return 400. Current get ratings returns a raw array, and summary returns { averageRating, ratingsCount }, not the Demo1.odt data wrapper/breakdown shape.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create Rating - Requester Rates Volunteer",
          "description": "Attempts to create a rating for a completed seeded assignment. With seeded data, the same rating may already exist; the smoke test accepts either 200 success or the repo's current 404 null result.",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status code is 200 or seeded duplicate 404', function () {",
